gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 128, Suns 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Suns, 128-103. Josh Giddey (23 points, seven rebounds, nine assists) and Chet Holmgren (20 points, six rebounds) totaled 43 points as Cason Wallace (16 points, 4-4 3PT) and Jalen Williams (16 points) added 32 more. Kevin Durant led Phoenix with 26 points and six rebounds.
